# Claude Code runtime artifacts. The lockfile coordinates CronCreate
# ownership across sessions in the same project; everything else under
# `.claude/` (skills, agents, etc.) is intentionally tracked.
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

# Design artifacts
**/design/

